* Optional: custom queues with authorization for principal 'app' (PoC defaults use DEV.QUEUE.1 / DEV.QUEUE.2 instead).
DEFINE QLOCAL('FACTORY.PIM') REPLACE
DEFINE QLOCAL('FACTORY.INSTRUCTIONS') REPLACE
SET AUTHREC PROFILE('FACTORY.PIM') OBJTYPE(QUEUE) PRINCIPAL('app') AUTHADD(PUT,GET,INQ)
SET AUTHREC PROFILE('FACTORY.INSTRUCTIONS') OBJTYPE(QUEUE) PRINCIPAL('app') AUTHADD(PUT,GET,INQ)
